üßæ Test Design ‚Äì Registration Form (Ticket Service)

üìå Description
This document provides test cases for the **registration form** of the Ticket Service project.  
The goal is to validate input fields using the techniques of **Equivalence Partitioning (EP)** and **Boundary Value Analysis (BVA)**.

The tested fields include:
- Name
- Surname
- Email
- Password
- Phone Number

Each test case checks both valid and invalid inputs to ensure the form handles data correctly and securely.

üß™ Test Cases ‚Äì Registration Form

| TC ID | Field      | Input                          | Expected Result                  | Class/Boundary          |
|-------|------------|--------------------------------|----------------------------------|-------------------------|
| TC01  | Name       | Alice                          | ‚úÖ Valid                         | EC Positive             |
| TC02  | Name       | A                              | ‚ùå Invalid (too short)           | BVA -1                  |
| TC03  | Name       | Al                             | ‚úÖ Valid                         | BVA Lower Bound         |
| TC04  | Name       | Alexander                      | ‚úÖ Valid                         | BVA Upper Bound (20)    |
| TC05  | Name       | AlexanderTheGreat123           | ‚ùå Invalid (too long)            | BVA +1                  |
| TC06  | Name       | Al!ce                          | ‚ùå Invalid (special chars)       | EC Negative             |
| TC07  | Surname    | Smith                          | ‚úÖ Valid                         | EC Positive             |
| TC08  | Surname    | S                              | ‚ùå Invalid (too short)           | BVA -1                  |
| TC09  | Surname    | Sm                             | ‚úÖ Valid                         | BVA Lower Bound         |
| TC10  | Surname    | Smithsonian                    | ‚úÖ Valid                         | BVA Upper Bound         |
| TC11  | Surname    | Smithsonian123456789           | ‚ùå Invalid (too long)            | BVA +1                  |
| TC12  | Surname    | Sm!th                          | ‚ùå Invalid (special chars)       | EC Negative             |
| TC13  | Email      | test@example.com               | ‚úÖ Valid                         | EC Positive             |
| TC14  | Email      | testexample.com                | ‚ùå Invalid (missing @)           | EC Negative             |
| TC15  | Email      | test@.com                      | ‚ùå Invalid (missing domain)      | EC Negative             |
| TC16  | Email      | te st@mail.com                 | ‚ùå Invalid (space)               | EC Negative             |
| TC17  | Password   | Pass123!                       | ‚úÖ Valid                         | EC Positive             |
| TC18  | Password   | password                       | ‚ùå Invalid (no digit/symbol)     | EC Negative             |
| TC19  | Password   | pass1234                       | ‚ùå Invalid (no uppercase/symbol) | EC Negative             |
| TC20  | Password   | PASS1234                       | ‚ùå Invalid (no symbol)           | EC Negative             |
| TC21  | Password   | P1!abcde                       | ‚úÖ Valid                         | BVA Lower Bound (8)     |
| TC22  | Password   | A1b2C3d4E5f6G7h8I9j!           | ‚úÖ Valid                         | BVA Upper Bound (20)    |
| TC23  | Password   | A1!b2c3d4e5f6g7h8i9j0K         | ‚ùå Invalid (21 chars)            | BVA +1                  |
| TC24  | Phone      | 0501234567                     | ‚úÖ Valid                         | EC Positive             |
| TC25  | Phone      | 123456789                      | ‚ùå Invalid (9 digits)            | BVA -1                  |
| TC26  | Phone      | 12345678901                    | ‚ùå Invalid (11 digits)           | BVA +1                  |
| TC27  | Phone      | 05012abc67                     | ‚ùå Invalid (letters inside)      | EC Negative             |

üîÑ Combined Input Test Cases ‚Äì Registration Form

‚úÖ Valid Combinations

These test combinations use valid data in all fields.

| Combo ID | Name       | Surname      | Email               | Password                  | Phone        | 
|----------|------------|--------------|---------------------|---------------------------|--------------|
